{"tid":654403,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"點解現代人得返智人一個物種 其他人種點解絕種？","createTime":"2018-05-05T15:20:26.000Z","updateTime":"2018-05-06T07:01:34.000Z","uid":2424,"like":11,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":33,"replies":[{"pid":"bbdb43c3ca2362aa6e76bc8325ee3c92821fbca1","tid":654403,"uid":2424,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-05T15:20:26.000Z","msg":"睇wiki先知原來遠古人屬仲有好多其他物種<br />\n例如尼安德塔人、匠人、澎湖原人<br />\n咁點解得返我地智人生存到？"},{"pid":"0b7a70f8f8bad70a25fc0846d693e4e73375dc68","tid":654403,"uid":106633,"like":0,"dislike":18,"score":-18,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-05T15:21:21.000Z","msg":"我花開後百花殺"},{"pid":"47c9ab36f0afa4a79dba9d270e97d04409af16f6","tid":654403,"uid":3500,"like":0,"dislike":7,"score":-7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-05T15:37:12.000Z","msg":"我記得人類大歷史呢本書有講到少少 但我唔記得左"},{"pid":"23fdc10a23ba8d9990cccd1e061eac77dfbd0ec7","tid":654403,"uid":2424,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"47c9ab36f0afa4a79dba9d270e97d04409af16f6","tid":654403,"uid":3500,"like":0,"dislike":7,"score":-7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-05T15:37:12.000Z","msg":"我記得人類大歷史呢本書有講到少少 但我唔記得左"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-05T15:44:04.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> bookmarked"},{"pid":"a5238b6438f142490d16e4214662a43474d062b1","tid":654403,"uid":3500,"like":14,"dislike":1,"score":13,"quote":{"pid":"23fdc10a23ba8d9990cccd1e061eac77dfbd0ec7","tid":654403,"uid":2424,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"47c9ab36f0afa4a79dba9d270e97d04409af16f6","tid":654403,"uid":3500,"like":0,"dislike":7,"score":-7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-05T15:37:12.000Z","msg":"我記得人類大歷史呢本書有講到少少 但我唔記得左"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-05T15:44:04.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> bookmarked"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-05T15:52:14.000Z","msg":"呢本書好野黎 解釋到好多我地心入面有關人類起源 文明演化 宗教作用 等等嘅問題 值得一睇再睇"},{"pid":"ce16b37a15df45ca9c745270a6ad44eb3542f47c","tid":654403,"uid":37869,"like":0,"dislike":0,"